strings: <se_low>*: I recently purchased a rattlesnake maid. Of course, you can't sell to everybody.

<se_low>*: I racked my brains tryin' to figure out a way to get rid of 'em.<page>*: And then I stumbled on an alchemy recipe to turn 'em into dragontail whips!<page>*: Can't tell you what it is, mind.
<se_low>*: I think I can give some advice. They are called "Dragon Tales" and appear to contain fragments of dragons that are actually dragons.
<se_low>*: That scared him until he couldn't sleep...he wanted a wife.
<se_def>*: Well that doesn't appear to be the case. Nothing crazy happened, I swear. Now don't be sad.
